Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:15.10,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最後的一步決定世界的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:19.08,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯一的贏家非我莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.61,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經親眼見證了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:28.70,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰都無從預知的最佳答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:33.62,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是在棋盤上操縱一切的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.24,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掀起思考的鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.78,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連錯誤也是偽裝的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.28,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至將死之前都在精心布局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.66,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是爭搶王位的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.25,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵從想法與欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.76,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次機會 在劫難逃的壞棋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:51.81,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後機會 勢必要擊潰勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.80,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.74,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅憑那種路數根本就無法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:58.88,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:04.28,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將完全勝利緊握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.10,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人都已望塵莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.79,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
