Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.02,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:04.93,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最初の一手で選ぶ 未知なるfuture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:08.85,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その有り様 this way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:15.10,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後の一手で決める 世界のanswer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:19.08,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一人のwinner it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.61,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この目は見据えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:28.70,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰も未だ見通せぬ最適解を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:33.62,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全ては盤上支配するgame
